<title>USA: Valmont CEO Bay named chairman.</title>
<headline>Valmont CEO Bay named chairman.</headline>
<dateline>VALLEY, Neb. 1996-12-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Valmont Industries Inc said Monday its president and chief executive officer Mogens Bay was named chairman, effective January 1.</p>
<p>He replaces Robert Daugherty, the companies founder, who is retiring but will remain a director, the lighting, communications and utility pole maker said.</p>
<p>Valmont shares fell 1/4 to 37-1/2 Monday.</p>
<p>((--Chicago newsdesk 312 408 8787)).</p>
